  <brief_title>A Clinical Study to Test Long Term Safety of GLPG1690 for Patients With Systemic Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open-label Extension Study to Evaluate the Long-term Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of Orally Administered GLPG1690 in Subjects With Systemic Sclerosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
