  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is the extension of the double-blind study GLPG1690-CL-204 (NCT03798366). The main
      purpose of the study is to see how GLPG1690 is tolerated in participants with systemic
      sclerosis and whether there are any side effects in a long-term treatment period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
